title: Searching for ADC Partner
body: I have played LoL since December 2015, I'm a support main and sadly highest elo ever reached has been B2. I'm searching for an ADC partner that is serious about partnering and dealing with my terribleness but is willing to work together. I am capable to use Skype to communicate with partner etc. ^-^ pm if anyone is interested

replies.body: Hey give us a pm on league, i'm a support main myself but i'm looking for a partner adc, I'm currently b4 myself.
